enhancement of diffusion is due to slow equilibration caused by\n(non-Abelian) hydrodynamic fluctuations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Jul 2020 18:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 4 Aug 2020 17:20:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 13 Nov 2020 02:13:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-27"}
