rference\nfrom imperfect hardware components. Subsequently, we overview several solutions\nfor 1-bit signal design to illustrate the gains achievable by exploiting CI.\nFinally, we identify some challenges and future research directions for 1-bit\nmassive MIMO systems that are yet to be explored.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Jul 2020 02:12:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 16 Dec 2020 01:37:20 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 23 Jan 2021 07:30:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-26"}
