 provides an important target for follow-up studies of\ndisks and accretion in very low mass stars, for example with ALMA and ESO-VLT\nX-Shooter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Jul 2020 10:17:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-14"}
