k on this problem. Finally, we study the simultaneous communication model\nand propose the first protocols with low per player information.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Jul 2020 13:36:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 12 Nov 2020 21:19:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-16"}
